.org/resource/Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"score\": 0.9999999742774438, \"rank\": 2.57224487536398e-08, \"text\": \"Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montigny-le-Bretonneux\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9719055496175848, \"rank\": 0.02859567600911666, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as ever it's not just track cycling on offer, with road racing and time trials,mountain biking,BMXracing and freestyling all also on the Olympic agenda once again this summer.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is the full 2024 Olympics cycling schedule (all times BST)...  13:30Women's individual time trial (road)  15:32Men's individual time trial (road)  13:10Women's cross-country mountain biking  13:10Men's cross-country mountain biking  12:25Women's BMX freestyle park qualification  14:11Men's BMX freestyle park qualification  12:10Women's BMX freestyle park final  13:44Men's BMX freestyle park final  19:00Men's BMX racing quarter-finals  19:20Women's BMX racing quarter-finals  21:05Men's BMX racing last chance race  21:15Women's BMX racing last chance race  19:00Men's BMX racing semi-finals  19:15Women's BMX racing semi-finals  20:35Men's BMX racing final  20:50Women's BMX racing final  10:00Men's road race  13:00Women's road race  16:00Women's team sprint qualifying  16:27Men's team pursuit qualifying  17:55Women's team sprint first round  18:09Men's team sprint qualifying  18:46Women's team sprint finals  16:30Women's team pursuit qualifying  